463" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1732627186463" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/collections/esterbrook-accessories?productListPgNo=1&productListFilters=product_type%3APen%20Cases" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/996adbc7-e4b2-4be6-a4b1-e175944032ba/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/tile-nook-cases.jpg" alt="Esterbrook Nook Cases" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1024" height="569" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1024" natural-height="569" data-lg-size="3000x3000" loading="lazy"></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1732627186493" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1732627186493"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><a href="/collections/esterbrook-accessories?productListPgNo=1&productListFilters=product_type%3APen%20Cases" class="">Nook Cases</a></h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1732627186459" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1732627186459"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>Made from British tan leatherette with contrasting white stitching, gold-hardware and brown and orange fabric lining patterned with the Esterbrook Eternity symbol, these are truly lovely things to add to your everyday carry to keep your pens and pencils safe.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="item"><div data-index="3" class="item-content"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675767638977" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver